  "body": "This issue follows [the comment](https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/pull/1091#discussion_r81823543) by @chriseth where he asked if there is an overflow possible from `SMOD` instruction.\n\nFor solving this, we need to [determine the SMOD semantics](https://github.com/ethereum/yellowpaper/issues/190) and then prove that SMOD does not cause an out-of-range value.\n",
